SCUD BUSTER - Relatively easy
-----------
VQAHEKU

Simple tips....PLEASE PAY ATTENTION to the mission info..if it says capture
or pick up a person when approaching the target fire missles one at a time
as you don't want to kill the person in the building....When you get to the
last part of SCUD BUSTER where you have to blow up the SCUD LAUNCHERS be
sure to blow the fuckers up RIGHT AWAY cuz a SCUD will be launched real
quick! And be sure to FOLLOW The missions in order...go out of order will
fuck you up....believe me.....don't blow up the SCUD commander
building..They have the flags out front...

