NUCLEAR STORM - Medium Difficulty - Last Screen
-------------
OTETEZT

This is the last and final screen....your first objective is to kill the
tanks that are in surrounding oil fields....besure to attack quick and don't
you or let the enemy blow any oil tanks up...3 strikes and your out on this
one pal....After that there is some people you have to rescue from the
bunkers..becareful and shot the missles right at the opening..besure not to
over fire killing the captives..after some other bullshit you have to blow
up some garbage trucks..take your time and wait for the right ones...it
takes sometime...then you get the Nuclear Scientist at the Nuclear
Plant...drop your copilot off at the Madmans palace....he gets
caught...madman goes to his bomber with your copilot....wait until the
fuckers are in the plane...and now set the hydras on and you to the front of
the plane and hit the very center of the cockpit BUT go to the right side of
the cockpit.....your copilot will come out grab him...now move away from the
plane....get involved in some action but don't let the plane outta
sight..when it start to move...HAUL ass to get in front of it...now stay ON
THE RUNWAY but be facing the plane..you will be going backwards and just
keep firing HELLFIRE at the son of a bitch and it will blow up...and thats
it...RETURN TO FRIGATE....

