OVERALL TIPS
------------
1) When blowing important buildings up that you have to pick someone up
   don't overfire...as to kill them also...

2) Blowing bunkers up...send missles right at the opening..don't overfire

3) Killing enemy choppers...best to use HYDRA's...having problems blowing
   shit up after firing 10,000 missles at it...get away from it...fly at
   it...go past it ..turn around and blow it up before it gets a lock...

4) TAKE YOUR TIME AND READ EVERYTHING IN THE MISSION DESCRIPTIONS..DO THEM
   IN ORDER...AND ON THE CONSOLE WHERE IT SAYS MISSIONS...READ THEM
   CAREFULLY...

